stories_text_raw:
As a user, I want to log issues, so that I can track and address problems efficiently.  
As a developer, I want to update validation rules, so that I can ensure data integrity and compliance.  
As a developer, I want to manage and cache D Files generation requests, so that I can optimize performance and resource usage.  
As a UI user, I want to report user testing results, so that I can provide feedback on the user experience.  
As a UI user, I want to begin user testing, so that I can evaluate the usability of the application.  
As a UI user, I want to redesign the Resources page, so that it matches the new styles and improves user engagement.  
As a data user, I want to process deletions for a specific date, so that I can maintain accurate data records.  
As a data user, I want to access FPDS data, so that I can perform necessary analyses and reporting.  
As an agency user, I want to include a large number of flexfields, so that I can customize data input without affecting performance.  
As a FABS user, I want to submit data, so that I can ensure compliance with reporting requirements.  
As a FABS user, I want to download uploaded FABS files, so that I can review the data submitted.  
As a broker user, I want to upload and validate error messages, so that I can ensure data integrity before processing.  
As a broker user, I want to generate a D1 file synced with FPDS data load, so that I can maintain consistency in reporting.  
As a system administrator, I want to process deletions for users of type DataUser, so that I can manage data efficiently.  
As a system administrator, I want to redesign the Resources page for UI users, so that the interface remains up to date.  
As a system administrator, I want to initiate user testing for UI users, so that I can gather user feedback effectively.
